{128}{}{伟大的。用水弄湿床单，塞住嘴放进嘴里，这样牙齿就不会受损。而且。。。好好的。 -- Great. Moisten your sheet with water, make a gag and put it in your mouth so your teeth won't be damaged. And also... Be well.}
